tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE neural_network_configurations (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    layers TEXT,
    activation_function VARCHAR(50),
    optimizer VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE neural_networks (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
name VARCHAR(255),
layers INT,
activation_function VARCHAR(50),
learning_rate FLOAT);

CREATE TABLE experiments (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
neural_network_id INT,
experiment_date DATE,
result VARCHAR(100));

CREATE TABLE experiments (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    neural_network_id INT NOT NULL,
    accuracy FLOAT,
    loss FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE hyperparameters (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT NOT NULL,
    learning_rate FLOAT,
    batch_size INT,
    epochs INT
);

CREATE TABLE neural_networks (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255),
  layers TEXT,
  optimizer VARCHAR(50),
  learning_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
  experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  neural_network_id INT,
  dataset_id INT,
  start_date DATETIME,
  end_date DATETIME
);

CREATE TABLE datasets (
  dataset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255),
  size_mb INT,
  num_features INT,
  num_classes INT
);

CREATE TABLE training_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id INT,
  training_loss FLOAT,
  validation_loss FLOAT,
  accuracy FLOAT
);
